<p>Pagination links indicate a series of related content exists across multiple pages. Typically these are used where a multi-page approach to long lists of content improves general performance, such as in search results or inboxes.</p>

<hr>
<h4>Default pagination</h4>

<p>Default pagination should be used on galleries that have multiple pages and search results.</p>

