<h4>Disabled and active states</h4>

<p>Links are customisable for different circumstances. Use <code>.disabled</code> for unclickable links and <code>.active</code> to indicate the current page.

{{> pagination-states}}
<span class="label label-default">Code</span>
<pre><code class="pattern-source html">{{> pagination-states}}</code></pre>

<p>You can optionally swap out active or disabled anchors for <code>&lt;span&gt;</code>, or omit the anchor in the case of the previous/next arrows, to remove click functionality while retaining intended styles.</p>

