<pre><code class="pattern-source html">{{> pagination-states-2}}</code></pre>




<hr>
<h4>Small pagination</h4>

<p>Remove <code>.pagination-lg</code> class to revert pagination to a smaller size. This sizing is to be used on internal web applications.</p>

